story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_0200_10:
However strong you may be, you have no chance
of winning against so many opponents. Don’t
you agree?
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_0400_10:
You don’t know anything about how an
organization should fight.
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_0600_10: Hmph! Go ahead—let’s see what you’ve got!
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_0800_10: What do you think you’re doing?!
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_0900_10: I’ll lend you two a hand.
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_1000_10: Let’s wrap this up efficiently, shall we?
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_1100_10:
Thank you for the help. It’s reassuring to have an
Elite Four member on our side.
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_1200_10: But look at all of them...
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_1300_10: I am now one extremely peeved Oleana!
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_1400_10:
Now now, you shouldn’t make a face like that.
Let’s treat them kindly...
story_final_02_04000/2401_1201_1500_10: and shower them with our endless love!
